Vampire," about a house invaded by vampires; and "Health Warning," which pits "traditionalist practitioners of martial arts against a neo-Nazi group bent on human engineering" sometime in the future. 
Lila Acheson Wallace Auditorium, 725 Park Ave. (212) 517-ASIA. 

